participants.name: Keith Rezendes
participants.title: CEO / Founder of MindSpree (building the largest social network of tutors and students) keith@mindspree.com

messages.message: Hey Brian, was hoping you join us for this ride. We would love to have you be a part of our team. We have tons of amazing ideas and i really want to hire the best 10 developers in AZ.

I am hoping to as well. I know that security is lacking on my resume and I want to read people's mindset at Schwab for the next 6 months so I can help make companies like yours unstoppable. You are very generous. I connected to the CIO at Arizona Board of Education. Anything you need me to pass along?
Sure, we are looking for investors other than that not sure. So if he knows anyone who is in our space. Send out way. Yeah, have fun and schwab, we will come and get you in 6 months.
We will come and chat in 6 months. Thanks for giving us the opportunity as well.
Thank you, I'll keep looking for people as well. I believe you and everyone else is a genius it is just a matter of realizing it.

Awesome contrarian thought.
I agree with that statement.
Also if you know of other senior developers looking for an amazing opportunity send our way.
I added. Is there a specific description I should use?
On my page. There's mindspree inc
Thx, trying to get mike to start. So in the future it is a hold up
I think he got yours setup
Thank you. I'll work on those old versions this weekend.
